# 📊 Dataset Information

The dataset contains medical features extracted from cancer patients.

### Dataset Features Include:

* Radius
* Texture
* Perimeter
* Area
* Smoothness
* Compactness
* Symmetry

### Target Variable

* Malignant (Cancerous)
* Benign (Non-Cancerous)

