# 🏗️ Neural Network Architecture

The Neural Network model consists of:

* Input Layer
* Hidden Dense Layers
* ReLU Activation Function
* Output Layer with Sigmoid Activation

### Optimizer

* Adam Optimizer

### Loss Function

* Binary Crossentropy

